      • parseSetting

      • parseCells

        public void parseCells()
        parse each grid on the map to a Cell object on a 2-D ArrayList "CellMap". Note: Waka and Ghosts are not parsed as Cells, but their initial positions will be registered in some Cells/Setting.

        Parameters:
        ambusherImg: - PImage of the Ambusher Ghost.
        chaserImg: - PImage of the Chaser Ghost.
